_sText:
**THE LAST PICTURE:** Added, because it could be funny, to look how it was looking before i started making it pretty and with details!:D

**GOOD TO KNOW:** The map is seriously bad, if there isn't auto bunny jump on the server!

**DETAILS:**

- You can walk into the wall behind the spawn and crouch in the window to shoot the enemy.
- To get in the tower, you need to stand under the pipe and then jump. You'll fly to the top.
- There is 2 ramps in the map, so if you get enaugh speed with the bunny jumping, then you can surf over them to get more fun!;)
- There is rounded walls on the long so you can easier bunny jump arround the map!
